channel.title: Dadmother - G A B B E R P E N T I N [gabber/hardcore/hardstyle]
channel.description:
Hey *HEY* **HEY**
I’m excited to unveil my first ever attempt at making a hardcore/hardstyle track! I’ve enjoyed the genre for a LONG time, but never tried to MAKE it.
**BUT NOW HERE WE ARE**
This a gabber goody that gets my blood pumping, and hopefully it does for you, too! Thanks for listening, and I hope you enjoy!
This is [G A B B E R P E N T I N](https://soundcloud.com/dadmother/g-a-b-b-e-r-p-e-n-t-i-n/s-fvyxp) ![image|500x500](upload://hf84cL4jC9WvNBvWk3wNMPGUlti.jpeg)
